item.title: CVE-2020-7808|2024-08-04T09:41:01.887Z -- raonwiz%20inc -- k%20upload
item.description: In RAONWIZ K Upload v2018.0.2.51 and prior, automatic update processing without integrity check on update module(web.js) allows an attacker to modify arguments which causes downloading a random DLL and injection on it.
